      • compareTo

        public int compareTo​(Episode second)
        Specified by:
        compareTo in interface java.lang.Comparable<Episode>
        Parameters:
        second - The second episode for which the first episode is to be compared to. The comparison will be done according to both season number, and which episode of that particular season
        Returns:
        The return type is given in either 0,1 or -1 (As is the case of episode). According to whether the episode is aired after, or before the first one.
